Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:44.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}记忆宛如昨日重现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:48.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}因为不想失去
